<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 18:14:37 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>世贸组织：中国对美国电动汽车和可再生能源税收抵免发起争议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/wto-china-initiates-dispute-over-us-tax-credits-evs-renewables-2024-03-28/</link><description>世界贸易组织周四表示，中国已与美国就《通胀削减法案》下的税收抵免启动争端磋商，以促进电动汽车和可再生能源的生产。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 15:59:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/wto-china-initiates-dispute-over-us-tax-credits-evs-renewables-2024-03-28/</guid></item><item><title>独家：中国商务部长将前往欧洲阐述电动汽车案例</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-commerce-minister-head-europe-make-ev-case-2024-03-28/</link><description>四名了解该计划的人士告诉路透社，中国商务部长将于四月前往欧洲，讨论欧盟委员会对中国电动汽车行业是否受益于不公平补贴的调查。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 12:56:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-commerce-minister-head-europe-make-ev-case-2024-03-28/</guid></item><item><title>生产商表示，中国对澳大利亚葡萄酒征收关税将损害波尔多葡萄酒的销售</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-duty-clear-australian-wine-will-hurt-bordeaux-sales-producers-say-2024-03-28/</link><description>法国波尔多葡萄酒出口商占中国葡萄酒和烈酒进口总量的9%，预计在中国周四决定提高对澳大利亚葡萄酒的进口关税后，出口将迅速下降。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 11:26:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-duty-clear-australian-wine-will-hurt-bordeaux-sales-producers-say-2024-03-28/</guid></item><item><title>报告称全球智能手机市场将于 2024 年反弹</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/global-smartphone-market-set-rebound-2024-report-says-2024-03-28/</link><description>Counterpoint Research 周四发布的一份报告称，由于通胀缓解有助于新兴市场的需求复苏，加上生成式人工智能的集成吸引买家购买高端设备，全球智能手机出货量预计今年将反弹 3%。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 11:14:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/global-smartphone-market-set-rebound-2024-report-says-2024-03-28/</guid></item><item><title>特斯拉交付量面临中国经济放缓和需求疲软的打击</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-deliveries-face-hit-china-slowdown-soft-demand-2024-03-28/</link><description>预计特斯拉下周将报告第一季度交付量低迷，原因是其降价带来的提振作用减弱，而且这家美国汽车制造商正在应对电动汽车市场放缓中买家的激烈竞争。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 09:37:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-deliveries-face-hit-china-slowdown-soft-demand-2024-03-28/</guid></item><item><title>中国取消对澳大利亚葡萄酒的关税，结束三年的贸易冻结</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-lifts-tariffs-australian-wine-bilateral-ties-recover-2024-03-28/</link><description>中国商务部周四表示，中国将从3月29日起取消对澳大利亚葡萄酒的反倾销和反补贴关税，结束三年的惩罚性关税，并向澳大利亚葡萄酒生产商提供期待已久的救济。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 08:27:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-lifts-tariffs-australian-wine-bilateral-ties-recover-2024-03-28/</guid></item><item><title>进口关税结束后富邑酒业将恢复在中国的分销</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/treasury-wine-resume-distribution-china-after-import-tariffs-end-2024-03-28/</link><description>在中国商务部表示将从 3 月 29 日起取消对澳大利亚葡萄酒进口的关税后，富邑葡萄酒集团 (Treasury Wine Estates) 周四表示，将恢复部分产品在中国的经销。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 08:25:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/treasury-wine-resume-distribution-china-after-import-tariffs-end-2024-03-28/</guid></item><item><title>阿里巴巴借菜鸟回购瞄准竞争对手海外进军</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/with-cainiao-buyback-alibaba-takes-aim-rivals-overseas-advance-2024-03-28/</link><description>分析师表示，阿里巴巴计划收购其物流子公司的全部控制权，而不是将其剥离，这可能表明这家中国巨头正在海外市场上更加认真地对待来自电子商务竞争对手 Shein 和 Temu 的竞争。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 08:01:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/with-cainiao-buyback-alibaba-takes-aim-rivals-overseas-advance-2024-03-28/</guid></item><item><title>工业园区称，中国比亚迪放缓了在越南建设电动汽车工厂的计划</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-slows-down-plans-ev-factory-vietnam-industrial-park-says-2024-03-28/</link><description>中国电动汽车制造商比亚迪已放慢了在越南建设电动汽车工厂的计划，该工厂所在工业园区的一位经理在周四的股东大会上表示。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 06:19:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-slows-down-plans-ev-factory-vietnam-industrial-park-says-2024-03-28/</guid></item><item><title>贸易部长表示，如果印度经济符合世贸组织规定，印度愿意加入中国贸易集团</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-open-joining-trade-blocs-with-china-if-its-economy-is-wto-compliant-trade-2024-03-28/</link><description>印度贸易部长皮尤什·戈亚尔 (Piyush Goyal) 在周四的一次媒体活动中表示，如果北京确保其经济开放、透明并遵守世界贸易组织的规则，印度愿意加入包括中国在内的贸易集团。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 06:09:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-open-joining-trade-blocs-with-china-if-its-economy-is-wto-compliant-trade-2024-03-28/</guid></item><item><title>马来西亚对将中国主导的铁路项目延伸至泰国边境持开放态度</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/malaysia-open-extending-china-led-rail-project-thai-border-2024-03-28/</link><description>马来西亚政府表示，将考虑将中国主导的价值100亿美元的铁路项目延伸至其与泰国的边境，以促进东南亚邻国之间的经济联系。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 05:25:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/malaysia-open-extending-china-led-rail-project-thai-border-2024-03-28/</guid></item><item><title>独家：美国情报官员告诉参议员，中国药明康德与北京共享美国客户的数据</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-wuxi-apptec-shared-us-clients-data-with-beijing-us-intelligence-officials-2024-03-28/</link><description>据两位消息人士透露，美国情报官员二月底告诉正在制定一项生物技术安全法案的参议员，中国制药公司药明康德在未经北京同意的情况下将美国知识产权转让给北京。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 05:04:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-wuxi-apptec-shared-us-clients-data-with-beijing-us-intelligence-officials-2024-03-28/</guid></item><item><title>受中国和日本销量下滑影响，丰田 2 月份全球销量下滑 7%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/toyotas-global-sales-slide-7-february-led-by-slumps-china-japan-2024-03-28/</link><description>丰田汽车2月份全球销量同比下降7%，原因是农历新年假期导致中国销量大幅下滑，以及小型汽车部门安全测试丑闻导致日本销量下滑。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 04:32:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/toyotas-global-sales-slide-7-february-led-by-slumps-china-japan-2024-03-28/</guid></item><item><title>中国五大银行利润率缩水，警告房地产风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-icbc-support-stabilisation-property-market-2024-03-28/</link><description>中国最大的五家银行公布净息差（NIM）不断缩小，同时对房地产行业持续存在的风险发出警告。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 04:16:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-icbc-support-stabilisation-property-market-2024-03-28/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾加大在中国争端中的赌注，誓言对海岸警卫队的“袭击”采取反制措施</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-defence-chief-reaffirms-support-philippines-chides-dangerous-chinese-conduct-2024-03-28/</link><description>菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯周四表示，菲律宾将对中国海警的“非法、胁迫、侵略性和危险的攻击”采取反制措施，这加大了南海争端不断升级的风险。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 03:49:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-defence-chief-reaffirms-support-philippines-chides-dangerous-chinese-conduct-2024-03-28/</guid></item></channel></rss>